&lt;/ul>
&lt;/li>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://pubs.opengroup.org/onlinepubs/9699919799/utilities/V3_chap02.html">Shell Command Language (pubs.opengroup.org)&lt;/a> &amp;hellip; 上と同じ内容のようだ&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
